---

<section class="bg-slate-800 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          My Proven Process for Automation Success
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Seven years of building successful automation systems has taught me exactly what works. 
          Here's the battle-tested process that delivers results every time.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Step 1: Discovery -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mb-4 mx-auto">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-blue-400">Discovery & Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-center mb-4">
              Deep dive into your current processes, pain points, and bottlenecks. I map out your entire workflow to identify automation opportunities.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-1">
              <li>• Process mapping sessions</li>
              <li>• Bottleneck identification</li>
              <li>• ROI calculation</li>
              <li>• Technical assessment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <!-- Arrow for larger screens -->
          <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-6 -right-4 text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 15.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L14.586 10l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414-1.414l5 5a1 1 0 010 1.414l-5 5a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Strategy -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-purple-600 rounded-full mb-4 mx-auto">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-purple-400">Strategic Planning</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-center mb-4">
              Design a custom automation strategy with clear priorities, timelines, and measurable outcomes. Every solution is built for your specific needs.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-1">
              <li>• Priority roadmap creation</li>
              <li>• Technology stack selection</li>
              <li>• Success metrics definition</li>
              <li>• Timeline planning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-6 -right-4 text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 15.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L14.586 10l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414-1.414l5 5a1 1 0 010 1.414l-5 5a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Development -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-green-600 rounded-full mb-4 mx-auto">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-green-400">Smart Development</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-center mb-4">
              Build robust, scalable automation using proven technologies and best practices. Regular updates keep you informed every step of the way.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-1">
              <li>• Agile development cycles</li>
              <li>• Regular progress updates</li>
              <li>• Comprehensive testing</li>
              <li>• Security-first approach</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-6 -right-4 text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 15.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L14.586 10l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 111.414-1.414l5 5a1 1 0 010 1.414l-5 5a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Optimization -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-600 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-orange-600 rounded-full mb-4 mx-auto">
              <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-orange-400">Deploy & Optimize</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 text-center mb-4">
              Launch your automation with comprehensive monitoring and continuous optimization. I ensure everything runs smoothly and delivers the promised ROI.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-slate-400 space-y-1">
              <li>• Smooth deployment process</li>
              <li>• Performance monitoring</li>
              <li>• User training & documentation</li>
              <li>• Ongoing optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Guarantee Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            My Automation Success Guarantee
          </h3>
          <p class="text-green-100 text-lg mb-6">
            I'm so confident in this process that I guarantee measurable ROI within 90 days of deployment. 
            If your automation doesn't deliver the promised results, I'll work with you at no charge until it does.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-white">
            <div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">90-Day</div>
              <div class="text-green-100 text-sm">ROI Guarantee</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">24/7</div>
              <div class="text-green-100 text-sm">System Monitoring</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Free</div>
              <div class="text-green-100 text-sm">30-Day Support</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>